item.description:
Join us to celebrate Barbara and Clay's wedding! No present is necessary. Your friendship is a gift!

The brunch menu includes Eggs Benedict, Crab Benny, Clancy's Corned Beef Hash & Poached Eggs
Chicken Oscar, Quiche Du Jour, Omelet Du Jour, and a Griddle Du Jour! Check out the brunch menu for yourself at http://clancysrestaurant.com

In addition to Brunch, the restaurant is also serves Soups, Salads, Burgers, Pasta, Sandwiches, and an exceptional Raw Bar in addition to many other selections!
